                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra, elements of the punctuation signs, of
                           the text dividers and of the quire marks; elements of Ethiopic
                           numerals.
 Several groups of lines on the incipit page of Text I-1,
                           alternating with black lines; two lines on the incipit page of Texts I-2,
                           I-3, and of subsections of Texts I-1, I-2, I-3 and I-4; initial two or
