                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#51ra">f. 51ra</locus>
                           <desc>: donation note. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#51ra">51ra</locus>: ዘመጽሐፍ፡ … ቆስቋም፡ ዘወሀበታ፡ አመተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡
                              ይኩኖ፡ …ትኪ፡ አመተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note is written in red ink and is partly illegible due to
                              faded ink. It states that ʾAmata ʾIyasus, whose name is written over
                              an erased name, is the donor of the book. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#54rb">f. 54rb</locus>
                           <desc>: donation note. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#54rb">54rb</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘማርያም፡ ጸበላ፡ ዘወሀበታ፡ አመተ፡
                              ኢየሱስ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥ[ል]ጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note states that ʾAmata ʾIyasus donated this book to Māryām
                              Ṣäbäla. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The abbreviated title ተ፡ ማ is written on <locus target="#1r">1r</locus> with azure paint.
 - Omitted letters
                           inserted interlineally: e.g., <locus target="#3va">3va</locus>, 13vb,
                           19va, 24rb, 39ra.
 - Omitted letter added at the beginning of the
                           line in the main hand: <locus target="#28ra">28ra</locus>.
 - Omitted
                           letter added at the end of the line in the main hand: <locus target="#32va">32va</locus>.
 - Erasures: e.g., <locus target="#8va">8va</locus>, 20vb, 35va.
 - Immediate corrections
                           indicated by dashes above and below the letters or the word: e.g., <locus target="#4va">4va</locus>, 11vb, 28ra, 40rb, 43vb.
 - Lacunae
                           (spaces for rubricated names left unfilled): e.g., <locus target="#23ra">23ra</locus>, 25vb, 47va, 49ra.
 - Pen trial: <locus target="#1v">1v</locus>, 2r.
 - Scribbles in pen or pencil: e.g., <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 2v, 23v, 51ra, 54v.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
