               <provenance>Additiones 1 and 2 mention ʾAmata ʾIyasus as
                     the donor.
 Several names are written in a secondary hand in the
                     supplication formulas: Gabra Masqal (e.g., 15rb,
                     19vb, 25vb, 37ra, 39va), ʾAmata ʾIyasus (e.g., 14va, 16vb, 30ra), ʾAmata Māryām (e.g., 16va, 23rb, 30rb) and Walatta Hāymānot (e.g., 17va, 23ra, 40vb, 47vb).</provenance></history>
